   Foreign Exchange:
   Dollar Tumbles on Greenspan's Hints
   Of Impending Interest-Rate Declines
   ----
   By Thomas L. Waite
   Special to The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/14/90
</DATE>
